description.p:
The alloy may advantageously contain other elements in very minor proportions. It comprises in particular:





silicon, as deoxidant for the molten metal during the smelting and molding of the alloy, preferably at an amount of less than 1.1%, or even less than 0.9%, or even less than 0.8% by weight;

manganese, also as deoxidant, preferentially at an amount of less than 0.9%, or even less than 0.6% by weight.
